maml:description.maml:para: Returns the time zone that has been set for the connected AppSense Management Server.
The Get-AppSenseManagementServerTimeZone cmdlet retrieves the time zone that has been set for the connected AppSense Management Server.
Sets the time zone of the AppSense Management Server that you would like to connect to.
The Set-AppSenseManagementServerTimeZone cmdlet sets the time zone that should be used when carrying out any operations or consistency checking on the AppSense Management Server.
A string representing the time zone of the AppSense Management Server.
When provided the time will also be output to any verbosely written line.
